{
  "id": "adv_card_chs_02_03",
  "title": "白石千紗 3話 自然体のステージ",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――ライブ当日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――The day of the live",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_church-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "church-00-night",
      "startTime": 1.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "千紗は楽しそうにメンバーとお喋りしているな\n本番直前でもさほど緊張していないようだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Chisa is chatting happily with the others.\nShe doesn’t look all that nervous‚ even this close to the start of the show.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.333333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_church-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "church-00-night",
      "startTime": 10.1333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_03-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "あ、{user}さん、お疲れ様です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ {user}-san. Is it that time already?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.133333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_church-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "church-00-night",
      "startTime": 13.6333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様。みんなともすっかり打ち解けたみたいだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hi. I can see that. You really become friends quickly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.633333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_03-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "はい、{user}さんのおかげです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ we have. Thanks to you‚ {user}-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_church-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "church-00-night",
      "startTime": 21.2666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_03-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "年上らしく振る舞えなくて悩んでた時に\n私らしいお姉さんになればいいって言ってくれて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When I was all hung up on acting as the onee-chan‚\nyou’re the one who told me to be myself.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.633333333333336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_church-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "church-00-night",
      "startTime": 28.8666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_03-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "そのおかげで\nみんなと自然体で付き合えるようになったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s what did it.\nNow I can just be myself with everyone.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "即席ユニットだからもっと緊張するかと思ったが\n四人ともリラックスしていい雰囲気じゃないか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I thought you’d be nervous because of how impromptu this team was‚\nbut the four of you seem real relaxed with good vibes.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.86666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_church-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "church-00-night",
      "startTime": 41.5666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_03-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "最初の頃はみんなグループの代表として恥ずかしい姿は\n見せられないって気を張っていたみたいなんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In the beginning‚ it seems all of them were worried\nabout making their original groups look bad.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.63333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_03-chs006.m4a",
      "text": "だから練習でも失敗しないように緊張して……\nそれなのに私だけはあれからずっと自然体で……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s why they were nervous about messing up even during practice…\nBut I’ve been keeping things natural ever since our talk.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.43333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_church-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "church-00-night",
      "startTime": 59.4666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_03-chs007.m4a",
      "text": "ダンスは上手じゃないし、喋るとすぐあたふたして\n全然格好付けようとしなくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m not a great dancer. I constantly trip over my tongue.\nAnd I didn’t put any effort into being cool.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_church-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "church-00-night",
      "startTime": 67.3333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_03-chs008.m4a",
      "text": "そんな私を見て、みんなの肩の力が抜けたらしいんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They saw me being myself‚ and that helped them all relax.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.33333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_church-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "church-00-night",
      "startTime": 72.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_03-chs009.m4a",
      "text": "無理して格好付けなくていいんだって分かって\n気持ちが楽になったって言われました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Once they realized they didn’t have to play it cool‚\nthey calmed down and started to enjoy themselves.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.26666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_church-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "church-00-night",
      "startTime": 79.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "千紗が素の自分を見せたことでみんなも心を開いたのか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ you being yourself helped them all open up.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "上からじゃなく同じ目線の高さでそばにいてくれる……\nそういうお姉さんらしさもあるのかもしれないな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rather than looking down on them‚ you stood with them eye to eye…\nThat sounds like something a onee-chan would do.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_church-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "church-00-night",
      "startTime": 93.3333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_03-chs010.m4a",
      "text": "私、今とっても楽しいんです\nこの四人でステージに立てることが嬉しいんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m really enjoying!\nBeing on stage with these three makes me so happy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.06666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_church-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "church-00-night",
      "startTime": 97.0666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_03-chs011.m4a",
      "text": "私達四人のステージを見ていて下さい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Please‚ watch the four of us in action!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_church-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "church-00-night",
      "startTime": 105.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_03-chs012.m4a",
      "text": "こころちゃん、すみれちゃん、すずちゃん\nもうすぐライブが始まるね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kokoro-chan‚ Sumire-chan‚ Suzu-chan!\nThe live is about to start.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_church-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "church-00-night",
      "startTime": 113.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_03-chs013.m4a",
      "text": "妹がいたらこんな感じなのかなって思いながら\n私はずっとみんなの頑張る姿を見てたんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ve been watching them all working so hard‚\nthinking this is what it must feel like to be a onee-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.83333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_03-chs014.m4a",
      "text": "だからなのかな？　いつもならライブ前は緊張するのに\n今日はそれ以上にみんなと歌うのが楽しみなんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Maybe that’s why I don’t feel nervous before performing like I usually do.\nI’m looking forward to singing with everyone!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.56666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_church-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "church-00-night",
      "startTime": 133.533333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_03-chs015.m4a",
      "text": "みんなのお姉さんとして今日は精一杯頑張るね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ll do my best today as their onee-chan!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_03-chs016.m4a",
      "text": "みなさん、こんばんは\n今夜は聖なる場所から私達四人で歌をお送りします",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good evening‚ everyone.\nToday we four are going to perform for you‚ here in this holy place.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.93333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_03-chs017.m4a",
      "text": "思い通りにいかなくて\n悩んだり辛かったりすることってありますよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sometimes things don’t go as planned.\nThey can be hard or difficult to understand.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_03-chs018.m4a",
      "text": "私達の歌が、そんなあなたの心の助けになりますように",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We hope our song can help soothe your heart!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_03-chs019.m4a",
      "text": "手をつないで、心を一つにして\n一夜限りの聖なるステージを始めます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Join hands‚ join hearts!\nOur one-night-only holy performance is about to start!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 164.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_03-chs020.m4a",
      "text": "真心を込めた天使の歌声が\n祝福となってあなたに届きますように……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We hope our sincere angelic singing voices\nwill reach you and bring you blessings.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 170.76666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（萎縮するでもなく、無理して背伸びするでもなく）\n（千紗は自然体で伸び伸びとパフォーマンスしている）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(She’s not nervous‚ but she’s also not overdoing it.)\n(Chisa’s making it her own. A completely natural performance.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 179.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "（年下の子達と組んだことは）\n（千紗を成長させるいい経験になったようだ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Teaming up with the younger girls has been good for her.)\n(Chisa has made some real progress.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 185.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_church-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "church-00-night",
      "startTime": 189.46666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様。いいライブだったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Great work. That was a good performance.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 190.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_03-chs021.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 193.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_church-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "church-00-night",
      "startTime": 195.86666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_03-chs022.m4a",
      "text": "私……今回のお仕事を通して思ったことがあるんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This job really taught me something important.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 195.86666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_church-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "church-00-night",
      "startTime": 201.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_03-chs023.m4a",
      "text": "最初は年上らしくしようとして\n無理して失敗しちゃったけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I tried to act like an onee-chan‚\nbut I couldn’t pull it off.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 205.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_03-chs024.m4a",
      "text": "私らしいお姉さんになればいいんだって気付いてからは\n凄く楽になって、うまく出来たんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Once I realized I should be my own version of a onee-chan‚\nit became lots of fun‚ and things clicked into place.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 212.36666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_church-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "church-00-night",
      "startTime": 216.36666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_03-chs025.m4a",
      "text": "誰かの真似じゃなくて、私らしく……\nそれが大切なんだって思いました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Not copying anyone else‚ just being myself…\nThat’s what’s important‚ isn’t it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 220.36666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_church-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "church-00-night",
      "startTime": 223.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_03-chs026.m4a",
      "text": "私はお姉ちゃんに追いつきたくて\nお姉ちゃんみたいなアイドルを目指してたけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I wanted to catch up with my own sister.\nI wanted to be an idol just like her.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 226.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_03-chs027.m4a",
      "text": "今回のことで、お姉ちゃんとは違うやり方で\nお姉ちゃんの横に並ぶ自分が見えた気がします",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But this has made me think I can stand alongside her\nby doing things my own way.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 234.23333333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_church-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "church-00-night",
      "startTime": 238.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_03-chs028.m4a",
      "text": "あ……す、すみません……\n私、生意気なこと言ってますよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah! S-sorry…\nI’m getting a bit full of myself‚ aren’t I?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 241.16666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_church-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "church-00-night",
      "startTime": 245.53333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_03-chs029.m4a",
      "text": "偉そうなことを言ってすみません\nお姉ちゃんが聞いたら呆れてたかも……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry for sounding so arrogant.\nMy onee-chan would shake her head in disappointment if she heard me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 248.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_church-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "church-00-night",
      "startTime": 252.03333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことはないさ\nきっと沙季も千紗を応援してくれるはずだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don’t think she would‚ Chisa.\nI’m sure Saki would support you proudly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 254.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_church-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "church-00-night",
      "startTime": 257.6666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "……なんだか千紗の話を聞いていたら\n麻奈と琴乃を思い出したよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Listening to you talk\nreminded me of Mana and Kotono.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 261.46666666666664,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_church-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "church-00-night",
      "startTime": 264.06666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_03-chs030.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈さん……ですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mana and Kotono?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 264.06666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_church-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "church-00-night",
      "startTime": 266.8333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃は姉の麻奈を追いかけてアイドルになり\nそこで姉とは違う自分の道を見つけて歩き始めた……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono became an idol‚ chasing after her sister Mana.\nAnd she found her own path forward.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 270.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_03-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "そんな琴乃の決断を麻奈が知ったら\nきっと独り立ちする妹を応援していたと思うんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If Mana found out about Kotono’s decision‚\nI’m sure she will support the independence of her sister.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 278.06666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_church-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "church-00-night",
      "startTime": 282.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_03-chs031.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈さんのことは遠い存在だと思ってましたけど\nそう聞くとなんだか身近に感じますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ve always thought Mana-san far away‚\nbut hearing that makes me feel closer to her.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 286.3666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_church-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "church-00-night",
      "startTime": 290.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_03-chs032.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈さんも私達と同じなんですね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She’s just like the rest of us‚ isn’t she?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 290.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_church-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "church-00-night",
      "startTime": 294.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_03-chs033.m4a",
      "text": "私は今回の経験を糧にして\nこれからもお姉ちゃんを目指していこうと思います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m going to take all the experience from this\nand use it to keep on working towards becoming a onee-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 298.76666666666665,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_03-chs034.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈さんと琴乃ちゃんみたいに、自分なりのやり方で\nお姉ちゃんの隣に立てるように頑張ります",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Just like Mana-san and Kotono-chan‚ I’m going to catch up\nto my own sister‚ but in my own way.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 306.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_church-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "church-00-night",
      "startTime": 310.1333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_03-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "その意気だ。俺も千紗を全力でサポートするよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s the spirit. I’m backing you all the way.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 310.1333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_church-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "church-00-night",
      "startTime": 314.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_03-chs035.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　ありがとうございます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Great! Thank you!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 314.8,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}